Wolfblade:

She transformed into bot mode and took the unit. "Hmm, yeah, this may 
just what we need. Now all we need is enough raw energon and a way to 
store in a battery to power this thing and give it the power to 
collapse into a black hole and we're good."  She lifted the unit up 
ont her shoulders. "OK, back to base then?"
